===Etymology===
From later {{etyl|fro}} ''[[coissin]]'' (modern ''[[coussin]]''), ultimately from {{etyl|la}} ''[[coxa]]'' via a {{etyl|VL.}} root *''coxinum'' ‘hip, thigh’ or alternatively from Latin {{term|culcita||mattress|lang=la}}.

